data.description: ***PRICE CHANGE AND SELLER CREDIT OF $2,500 TOWARD CLOSING COSTS***Discover the epitome of comfort in this charming 3-bed, 1-bath home spanning 1,084 sq ft. Revel in the allure of new interior paint and laminate flooring throughout, creating a modern aesthetic. The white kitchen, adorned with pristine appliances, exudes timeless elegance. A one-car detached garage adds convenience. Nestled in a prime location within an established neighborhood, the property boasts a serene backdrop with open space behind the backyard. Embrace a lifestyle of tranquility and style in this meticulously crafted haven.
